1
00:00:17,208 --> 00:00:17,666
- ( Avatars yelling )
- ( grunts )

2
00:00:17,750 --> 00:00:19,333
- ( all grunt )

3
00:00:19,416 --> 00:00:24,166
- ( gasps )
- ( female Avatars shout )

4
00:00:24,250 --> 00:00:25,708
- I'LL KEEP THEM
TIED UP HERE.

5
00:00:25,791 --> 00:00:27,750
- YOU GUYS GO ON 
AHEAD WITHOUT ME.

6
00:00:40,833 --> 00:00:42,125
- ( gasps )

7
00:00:42,208 --> 00:00:43,500
- ( siren blares )

8
00:00:43,583 --> 00:00:44,583
- THEY MUST HAVE CHANGED
THE PASSWORD.

9
00:00:44,666 --> 00:00:46,708
- HOW DID THEY KNOW?

10
00:00:48,083 --> 00:00:49,333
- THESE PEOPLE
ARE YOUR FRIENDS.

11
00:00:49,416 --> 00:00:51,000
HOW CAN YOU BETRAY THEM
SO EASILY?

12
00:00:51,083 --> 00:00:52,250
- ( chuckles )

13
00:00:52,333 --> 00:00:54,333
WHO NEEDS THEM
WHEN I HAVE YOU?

14
00:00:54,416 --> 00:00:56,500
- ( grunts, gasps )

15
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:01,916
YOU SHOULD RUN
WHILE YOU STILL CAN.

16
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,875
- I'LL LET GO.
- NO.

17
00:01:03,958 --> 00:01:06,041
SOMEONE DRAINED ALL
THE SHAMPOO AND CONDITIONER.

18
00:01:06,125 --> 00:01:07,625
- ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

19
00:01:07,708 --> 00:01:09,833
THAT MEANS WE CAN'T HIDE
BEHIND THE BUBBLES NOW. 

20
00:01:12,208 --> 00:01:13,583
- IT'S TIME, MS. TOUDOU.

21
00:01:13,666 --> 00:01:15,500
WE HAVE NO CHOICE
BUT TO ESCAPE.

22
00:01:15,583 --> 00:01:19,291
- ( groans )
DAMN THAT PROBATIONARY STUDENT!

23
00:01:19,375 --> 00:01:21,708
- ( all scream )

24
00:01:21,791 --> 00:01:25,375
- NO WAY. SHE'S GOT THE WEIRD
BURN MARK ON HER BUTT.

25
00:01:25,458 --> 00:01:27,875
- SHE MUST BE THE SCUMBAG
THAT WAS TRYING TO BLACKMAIL US.

26
00:01:27,958 --> 00:01:30,791
- SO, AKIHISA DIDN'T SET UP 
THE HIDDEN CAMERA AFTER ALL?

27
00:01:30,875 --> 00:01:32,375
OH, THAT'S SUCH A RELIEF.

28
00:01:32,458 --> 00:01:34,041
- I'M REALLY SORRY, AKI.
WE WERE WRONG.

29
00:01:34,125 --> 00:01:37,708
- IT'S OKAY.  AS LONG AS YOU
FEEL BAD ABOUT IT.

30
00:01:37,791 --> 00:01:39,458
- WELL, YOU WIN.

31
00:01:39,541 --> 00:01:41,708
I'VE DECIDED TO LET YOU
SPY ON THE GIRLS ALL YOU WANT.

32
00:01:43,458 --> 00:01:44,791
- All: YEAH!

33
00:01:44,875 --> 00:01:46,916
PARADISE, HERE WE COME!

34
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,958
- ( gasps )

35
00:01:49,041 --> 00:01:51,250
- Fukuhara: THE WHOLE THING
WAS JUST A DREAM.

36
00:01:51,333 --> 00:01:55,250
THIS WOULD BE THE THIRD NIGHT
OF ACADEMIC TRAINING CAMP.

37
00:01:56,583 --> 00:01:58,541
- DAMN.
IT'S NOT FAIR.

38
00:01:58,625 --> 00:02:01,250
WHY DID MS. TAKAHASHI
HAVE TO BUTT INTO OUR BUSINESS?

39
00:02:01,333 --> 00:02:03,125
- SHE'S TOO STRONG.
IT'S CHEATING.

40
00:02:03,208 --> 00:02:05,083
- HOW ARE YOU
GONNA HANDLE IT?

41
00:02:05,166 --> 00:02:06,333
I MEAN, YOU'VE GOT
TO DO SOMETHING

42
00:02:06,416 --> 00:02:07,750
IF YOU WANT TO GET OUT
FROM UNDER

43
00:02:07,833 --> 00:02:09,916
THE BLACKMAILER'S CONTROL.
- I KNOW.

44
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,166
WE'RE NOT GIVING UP YET.

45
00:02:11,250 --> 00:02:12,833
- YEAH, BUT TOMORROW IS

46
00:02:12,916 --> 00:02:13,916
THE LAST NIGHT TO CATCH THEM.

47
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,791
- I'VE ALREADY GOT ANOTHER PLAN.

48
00:02:15,875 --> 00:02:18,833
ALTHOUGH, I DON'T THINK
THE GUYS FROM D, E, AND F

49
00:02:18,916 --> 00:02:21,250
ARE GONNA BE ENOUGH. WE'LL STILL
NEED A LOT MORE BACK-UP.

50
00:02:21,333 --> 00:02:23,791
ARE YOU WITH ME, KOUTA?
- I'LL HANDLE THE PHOTOGRAPHY.

51
00:02:23,875 --> 00:02:26,875
- AKIHISA, YOUR JOB'S TO LURE
THE GIRLS TO OUR ROOM.

52
00:02:26,958 --> 00:02:28,500
- BUT WHY?
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

53
00:02:28,583 --> 00:02:30,833
- IF WE CAN JUST GET
A COUPLE OF PICTURES OF THEM,

54
00:02:30,916 --> 00:02:32,500
THEN WE CAN USE THOSE
PICTURES AS BAIT

55
00:02:32,583 --> 00:02:34,333
TO REQUEST HELP FROM
THE OTHER CLASSES.

56
00:02:34,416 --> 00:02:36,416
- YEAH, I GET IT.
WE'LL CONVINCE THE OTHER GUYS

57
00:02:36,500 --> 00:02:38,708
TO HELP US BY APPEALING
TO THEIR ANIMAL DESIRES

58
00:02:38,791 --> 00:02:39,875
WITH THE PICTURES.

59
00:02:39,958 --> 00:02:41,875
- AND HERE IS A YUKATA
FOR YOUR PICTURE.

60
00:02:41,958 --> 00:02:44,208
- NO, WE'RE TAKING
PICTURES OF THE GIRLS.

61
00:02:46,791 --> 00:02:49,291
- I'LL SEND HIMEJI
AND MINAMI A TEXT MESSAGE.

62
00:02:49,375 --> 00:02:51,625
"I'VE GOT SOMETHING
I WANT TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT.

63
00:02:51,708 --> 00:02:55,333
CAN YOU COME TO MY ROOM
ASAP?"  AND SEND.

64
00:02:55,416 --> 00:02:56,333
- ( phone beeps )

65
00:02:56,416 --> 00:02:58,458
- HIMEJI NEVER
LEAVES ME WAITING.

66
00:02:58,541 --> 00:03:00,458
- "I'LL LEAVE IN
A FEW MINUTES.

67
00:03:00,541 --> 00:03:02,875
I'VE JUST GOT TO PACK UP A FEW
SNACKS FOR US FIRST, 'KAY?"

68
00:03:02,958 --> 00:03:05,291
- OH, COOL.
MINAMI REPLIED TOO.

69
00:03:05,375 --> 00:03:07,708
- "YEAH, I GUESS I CAN.
BUT WHY THIS LATE?

70
00:03:07,791 --> 00:03:09,291
CAN'T IT WAIT
TILL TOMORROW?"

71
00:03:09,375 --> 00:03:11,041
- SOUNDS LIKE SHE'S
PLAYING IT SAFE.

72
00:03:11,125 --> 00:03:13,291
HOW SHOULD I RESPOND?
- ( phone beeps )

73
00:03:13,375 --> 00:03:16,458
- HUH, ANOTHER ONE?
AND IT'S FROM SUGAWA.

74
00:03:16,541 --> 00:03:19,791
- "HEY, I WAS WONDERING,
WHY ARE YOU GUYS SO DESPERATE

75
00:03:19,875 --> 00:03:21,458
TO SPY ON THE NAKED GIRLS?"

76
00:03:21,541 --> 00:03:23,666
- REALLY?
OH, COME ON.

77
00:03:23,750 --> 00:03:25,666
THAT QUESTION PRACTICALLY
ANSWERS ITSELF.

78
00:03:25,750 --> 00:03:28,083
"YOU KNOW WHY.
IT MAY BE DESPERATE,

79
00:03:28,166 --> 00:03:31,333
BUT THE HEART WANTS
WHAT THE HEART WANTS."

80
00:03:31,416 --> 00:03:33,000
HMM?  HMM?

81
00:03:34,875 --> 00:03:36,708
AAH!

82
00:03:36,791 --> 00:03:39,333
CALM DOWN, AKIHISA, BUDDY.

83
00:03:39,416 --> 00:03:41,708
LET'S PLAY THIS BACK
STEP BY STEP.

84
00:03:44,541 --> 00:03:45,875
AAH!

85
00:03:45,958 --> 00:03:47,500
- HEY, IS SOMETHING WRONG,
AKIHISA?

86
00:03:47,583 --> 00:03:51,208
( grunts )

87
00:03:51,291 --> 00:03:52,833
IS THERE ANYTHING
I CAN HELP YOU WITH?

88
00:03:52,916 --> 00:03:54,083
YOU LOOK KIND OF DOWN.

89
00:03:54,166 --> 00:03:55,500
- COULD YOU MAYBE
GO BACK IN TIME

90
00:03:55,583 --> 00:03:56,875
AND <i>NOT</i> BREAK MY PHONE?

91
00:03:56,958 --> 00:03:58,375
- QUIT WORRYING.
I GOT IT.

92
00:03:58,458 --> 00:03:59,916
I'LL HAVE THIS THING
FIXED UP IN NO TIME.

93
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,125
- LET ME BORROW YOUR CELL.
NOW, DAMN IT!

94
00:04:02,208 --> 00:04:03,750
- SURE, MAN.

95
00:04:03,833 --> 00:04:06,541
- I NEED TO EXPLAIN 
THAT TEXT TO MINAMI.

96
00:04:06,625 --> 00:04:08,458
YOUR CONTACTS ARE EMPTY.

97
00:04:08,541 --> 00:04:10,541
YOU KNOW YOU'VE ONLY GOT
SHOUKO'S CONTACT INFO IN HERE?

98
00:04:10,625 --> 00:04:12,375
- WHAT?!  DAMN IT.

99
00:04:12,458 --> 00:04:14,375
I'VE GOTTA FIND A NEW PLACE
TO HIDE MY PHONE.

100
00:04:14,458 --> 00:04:15,958
I WISH SHE WOULD
STOP DOING THAT.

101
00:04:16,041 --> 00:04:17,625
- YEAH,
THAT'S KIND OF MESSED UP.

102
00:04:17,708 --> 00:04:19,458
YOU DON'T HAPPEN TO KNOW
MINAMI'S NUMBER, DO YOU?

103
00:04:19,541 --> 00:04:22,041
- OH YEAH, SURE.  THE SAME WAY
YOU KNOW SHOUKO'S NUMBER.

104
00:04:22,125 --> 00:04:23,958
- WELL, I GUESS IT WAS
WORTH ASKING.

105
00:04:24,041 --> 00:04:27,125
- HOLD ON.
WHAT DID YOU JUST SEND?

106
00:04:27,208 --> 00:04:28,500
AAH!

107
00:04:32,791 --> 00:04:35,375
YOU JUST TOOK A GIANT DUMP
ON MY LIFE, YOU MORON!

108
00:04:35,458 --> 00:04:36,583
- NOW YOU KNOW HOW I FEEL.

109
00:04:36,666 --> 00:04:38,791
AND YOU CAUSED THAT
FEELING, YOU JERK!

110
00:04:38,875 --> 00:04:40,333
- SHUT THE HELL UP!

111
00:04:40,416 --> 00:04:43,000
- ( boys gasp )
YES, SIR.

112
00:04:43,083 --> 00:04:45,166
- THIS IS BAD.
I'VE GOTTA FIX IT.

113
00:04:45,250 --> 00:04:47,083
I NEED YOUR CELL
TO CALL SHOUKO. 

114
00:04:47,166 --> 00:04:49,750
- I DROPPED MINE IN THE TOILET
AND CAN'T AFFORD A NEW ONE.

115
00:04:49,833 --> 00:04:51,625
- YOU KNOW THE GOVERNMENT
CAN TRACK YOU WITH THOSE THINGS.

116
00:04:51,708 --> 00:04:55,708
- IT'S OVER.
MY LIFE IS COMPLETELY OVER.

117
00:04:55,791 --> 00:04:57,916
- ( knocks on door )
- IT'S OPEN.

118
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,000
- HEY, WHAT'S UP, YOU GUYS?
- HEY, HIMEJI.

119
00:05:00,083 --> 00:05:02,166
GLAD YOU COULD MAKE IT. 
BUT HOW DID YOU MAKE IT?

120
00:05:02,250 --> 00:05:03,833
DIDN'T IRON MAN 
TRY TO STOP YOU?

121
00:05:03,916 --> 00:05:06,666
- I GAVE HIM A COUPLE OF SNACKS
AND HE LET ME THROUGH.

122
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:10,125
- MAY FLIGHTS OF ANGELS
SING HIM TO HIS REST.

123
00:05:10,208 --> 00:05:11,750
- WELL, I'M HERE, AKIHISA.

124
00:05:11,833 --> 00:05:13,250
WHAT DID YOU WANT TO
TALK TO ME ABOUT?

125
00:05:13,333 --> 00:05:16,416
- Akihisa: OH, YEAH.
I'M GLAD YOU BROUGHT THAT UP.

126
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:18,541
- ( camera shutter clicks )

127
00:05:20,666 --> 00:05:22,000
- Fukuhara:
WITH THE PICTURES TAKEN

128
00:05:22,083 --> 00:05:23,416
AND THEIR GOAL COMPLETED,

129
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:25,583
THE NIGHT COULDN'T GET
ANY BETTER.

130
00:05:25,666 --> 00:05:27,375
HOWEVER...

131
00:05:30,791 --> 00:05:33,166
- HEY, AKI.  AKI.

132
00:05:34,958 --> 00:05:37,041
YOU ASLEEP?

133
00:05:37,125 --> 00:05:39,583
HEY.  WAKE UP, JERKWAD.

134
00:05:39,666 --> 00:05:41,041
- HMM?

135
00:05:41,125 --> 00:05:43,000
- I CAME TO YOUR ROOM
LIKE YOU SAID.

136
00:05:45,708 --> 00:05:48,583
THIS WAS YOUR IDEA.
NOW GO AND WAKE UP.

137
00:05:48,666 --> 00:05:50,208
- ( bones crack )
- ( screams )

138
00:05:50,291 --> 00:05:51,625
- SHH!

139
00:05:51,708 --> 00:05:53,625
SHUT UP, AKI.
YOU'RE BEING TOO LOUD.

140
00:05:53,708 --> 00:05:55,458
-  ( muffled screams )

141
00:05:55,541 --> 00:05:57,458
( groans )

142
00:05:57,541 --> 00:05:59,500
- WELL, DON'T JUST
GO BACK TO SLEEP! 

143
00:06:00,958 --> 00:06:03,875
- MINAMI, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING IN HERE?

144
00:06:03,958 --> 00:06:06,041
( gasps ) I THINK I MIGHT
KNOW THE ANSWER TO THAT.

145
00:06:06,125 --> 00:06:09,041
ONE, I SENT MINAMI
A WEIRD-ASS TEXT. 

146
00:06:09,125 --> 00:06:10,916
- ( groans )
- TWO, KNOWING HER,

147
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,791
SHE'S PROBABLY PISSED OFF.

148
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:15,083
THREE, SHE'S LOOMING OVER
MY SLEEPING BODY.

149
00:06:15,166 --> 00:06:18,333
FOUR, HER BODY'S A WEAPON.
- AAH!

150
00:06:18,416 --> 00:06:20,166
- THERE YOU HAVE IT.

151
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:23,250
JUST PLEASE TRY TO MAKE IT
QUICK AND PAINLESS, OKAY. 

152
00:06:23,333 --> 00:06:24,791
- TO BE HONEST, I'M NOT
SURE I WANT TO KNOW

153
00:06:24,875 --> 00:06:26,333
WHAT THAT'S SUPPOSED TO MEAN.

154
00:06:26,416 --> 00:06:27,583
- WHAT?
YOU MEAN I'M SAFE?

155
00:06:30,125 --> 00:06:32,333
- I DON'T GET YOU.
IT'S NOT LIKE IT WAS EASY

156
00:06:32,416 --> 00:06:33,666
FOR ME TO COME OVER HERE,
YOU KNOW.

157
00:06:33,750 --> 00:06:36,791
- ( gasps )
- SO THEN... I...

158
00:06:36,875 --> 00:06:39,250
I WANT YOU TO
TELL ME IN PERSON,

159
00:06:39,333 --> 00:06:40,666
NOT BY TEXT,

160
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,708
BEFORE I LET THIS THING
GO ANY FURTHER.

161
00:06:42,791 --> 00:06:46,083
- THAT'S A LOT OF PRESSURE
TO COME UP WITH MY FINAL WORDS.

162
00:06:46,166 --> 00:06:47,500
( gasps )

163
00:06:47,583 --> 00:06:49,541
I COULD USE
SOME HELP RIGHT NOW.

164
00:06:49,625 --> 00:06:51,833
HIDEYOSHI LOOKS TOO CUTE
TO WAKE UP.

165
00:06:51,916 --> 00:06:54,666
KOUTA'S WRAPPED UP
TAKING PICTURES, OF COURSE.

166
00:06:54,750 --> 00:06:57,291
YUUJI'S BEING TIED UP
AND MOLESTED BY SHOUKO.

167
00:06:57,375 --> 00:06:59,125
-  ( muffled scream )
- DAMN IT.

168
00:06:59,208 --> 00:07:00,875
DON'T MY FRIENDS REALIZE
I NEED THEM?

169
00:07:00,958 --> 00:07:02,333
- ( muffled screams )

170
00:07:02,416 --> 00:07:04,708
- I'VE COME TO RESCUE YOU,
MY DARLING LOVE.

171
00:07:04,791 --> 00:07:08,333
AAH!
- THERE'S SOMETHING BEHIND YOU!

172
00:07:08,416 --> 00:07:11,125
- MIHARU, WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING IN HERE? 

173
00:07:11,208 --> 00:07:13,291
- I CREPT INTO YOUR BED
TO SURPRISE YOU

174
00:07:13,375 --> 00:07:14,750
ONLY TO FIND THAT
IT WAS EMPTY.

175
00:07:14,833 --> 00:07:16,416
AND WHERE ELSE
COULD YOU HAVE GONE?

176
00:07:16,500 --> 00:07:17,958
- WE TALKED ABOUT THIS
YESTERDAY,

177
00:07:18,041 --> 00:07:19,375
YOU LITTLE LUNATIC!
- HUH?

178
00:07:19,458 --> 00:07:20,958
YOU TRIED THIS YESTERDAY TOO?

179
00:07:21,041 --> 00:07:23,291
- COME ON, BABY.
LET'S GO TO OUR ROOM

180
00:07:23,375 --> 00:07:25,375
AND COIL OUR
NAKED BODIES TOGETHER.

181
00:07:25,458 --> 00:07:26,708
DON'T GO THINKING
YOU'LL BE GETTING

182
00:07:26,791 --> 00:07:28,541
ANY SLEEP TONIGHT THOUGH.

183
00:07:28,625 --> 00:07:30,125
NOW FOLLOW ME.  COME ON.
- ( screams )

184
00:07:30,208 --> 00:07:32,375
- I DON'T KNOW WHY YOU
TRY TO RESIST ME.

185
00:07:32,458 --> 00:07:34,208
- GET COMFORTABLE.
YOU'RE NOT SLEEPING EITHER.

186
00:07:34,291 --> 00:07:37,166
- ( gasps )

187
00:07:37,250 --> 00:07:40,166
- WHY IS EVERYBODY SCREAMING?

188
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:42,083
- SHUT UP, GUYS.
KEEP IT DOWN.

189
00:07:42,166 --> 00:07:43,666
IF YOU ALL GET ANY LOUDER,
THEN--

190
00:07:43,750 --> 00:07:45,458
- Nishimura: HEY!
- ( gasps )

191
00:07:45,541 --> 00:07:47,583
- WHAT THE HELL IS
ALL THIS RUCKUS?

192
00:07:47,666 --> 00:07:49,750
- MAN, WE ARE IN
DEEP CRAP HERE. 

193
00:07:49,833 --> 00:07:51,833
- HE'S GONNA KILL US WHEN HE
SEES FOUR HALF-NAKED GIRLS

194
00:07:51,916 --> 00:07:53,500
IN OUR ROOM.
- THERE'S ONLY THREE,

195
00:07:53,583 --> 00:07:55,166
OR AM I MISSING ONE?

196
00:07:55,250 --> 00:07:57,583
- YUUJI AND I ARE GONNA
TRY TO DISTRACT HIM.

197
00:07:57,666 --> 00:07:59,000
YOU GIRLS MAKE A RUN FOR IT
WHILE WE DO.

198
00:08:01,125 --> 00:08:02,333
LET'S GO.
- YEAH.

199
00:08:02,416 --> 00:08:05,250
- ( panting, squeals )

200
00:08:05,333 --> 00:08:07,666
- I HOPE YOU'RE PREPARED
FOR YOUR DESTRUCTION, YOSHII.

201
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:10,583
- ( grunts )
I TRY NOT TO THINK ABOUT THAT.

202
00:08:10,666 --> 00:08:12,583
- THEN PREPARE TO
GET PREPARED!

203
00:08:12,666 --> 00:08:14,666
- HE'S ON OUR ASS.
OUR ONLY HOPE IS TO HIDE

204
00:08:14,750 --> 00:08:16,625
SOMEPLACE HE CAN'T GO.
- AND WHERE IS THAT?

205
00:08:16,708 --> 00:08:18,625
- THE GIRL'S ROOM.
- I GET YOU.

206
00:08:18,708 --> 00:08:20,375
IRON MAN CAN'T GO INTO
THE GIRL'S ROOM

207
00:08:20,458 --> 00:08:22,291
'CAUSE HE'S A GUY
AND HE'LL GET FIRED.

208
00:08:22,375 --> 00:08:24,375
BUT IF I GO IN THERE WEARING
NOTHING BUT MY UNDERWEAR,

209
00:08:24,458 --> 00:08:27,291
THEN I'LL MOST LIKELY
GET SENT TO PRISON.

210
00:08:27,375 --> 00:08:29,125
- LET'S RISK IT.
- NO FREAKING WAY.

211
00:08:29,208 --> 00:08:30,958
- IF YOU'RE GONNA ACT LIKE
SUCH A GIRL ABOUT IT,

212
00:08:31,041 --> 00:08:33,666
PUT THIS ON AND SHUT UP.
- THANK YOU.

213
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:36,125
-  ( screams )
- OKAY, THERE IT IS.

214
00:08:36,208 --> 00:08:38,291
WE'RE ALMOST IN THE CLEAR.
- HOLD ON.

215
00:08:38,375 --> 00:08:40,416
I'D BE BETTER OFF GOING IN THERE
BUCK NAKED THAN WEARING THIS.

216
00:08:40,500 --> 00:08:42,625
- YOU MAKE AN EXCELLENT POINT,
BUDDY.

217
00:08:42,708 --> 00:08:44,958
GOOD LUCK.
- GET BACK HERE.

218
00:08:45,041 --> 00:08:46,250
- LOOK, I'D RATHER
NOT GET BUSTED

219
00:08:46,333 --> 00:08:47,791
WITH A CROSS-DRESSER, OKAY?

220
00:08:47,875 --> 00:08:49,750
- THEN I GUESS YOU'D BETTERd
GIVE ME YOUR YUKATA.

221
00:08:49,833 --> 00:08:52,291
- GET OFF ME, YOU FREAK.
- DO IT.

