235
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:24,166
- WE'VE GOT COUNSELING WITH IRON
MAN FOR THREE DAYS IN A ROW.

236
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:26,291
- YOU HAVE TO ADMIT,
