238
00:09:28,583 --> 00:09:32,333
- WHOA!
YOU ARE FREAKING AMAZING, DUDE.

239
00:09:32,416 --> 00:09:34,416
- OKAY, GUYS.
IT'S TIME.

240
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:36,416
LET'S GO FIND SOME
RECRUITS TO HELP US.

241
00:09:36,500 --> 00:09:39,875
- Fukuhara: THE FOURTH DAY
