THEY CANCEL EACH OTHER OUT.

257
00:10:18,458 --> 00:10:20,333
- I SEE.
I GUESS IT MUST CAUSE

258
00:10:20,416 --> 00:10:22,000
TOO MUCH TECHNICAL
INTERFERENCE.

259
00:10:22,083 --> 00:10:23,500
- THIS IS OUR LAST CHANCE.

260
00:10:23,583 --> 00:10:24,833
THEY'LL DO EVERYTHING THEY CAN

261
00:10:24,916 --> 00:10:26,583
TO CREATE AN UNBREAKABLE
LINE OF DEFENSE.

262
00:10:28,083 --> 00:10:29,500
WHILE AVOIDING THE INTERFERENCE,

263
00:10:29,583 --> 00:10:30,750
THEY'RE GOING TO STAGGER
THEIR MAIN FORCES

264
00:10:30,833 --> 00:10:32,916
BY THE LEVEL OF THEIR STRENGTH.

265
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,833
THIS IS THEIR
EXPECTED FORMATION.

266
00:10:34,916 --> 00:10:36,416
- OUR ROOM IS HERE 
ON THE THIRD FLOOR,

267
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,750
WHILE OUR GOAL LIES
DEEP IN THE BASEMENT.

268
00:10:38,833 --> 00:10:41,083
- MS. TAKAHASHI,
MR. OOSHIMA, AND IRON MAN

269
00:10:41,166 --> 00:10:42,750
