DEFENDING THE BASEMENT,

270
00:10:42,833 --> 00:10:44,416
WHILE ON THE OFFENSIVE FRONT,

271
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:46,291
WE'VE GOT THE GUYS
FROM D, E, AND F. 

272
00:10:46,375 --> 00:10:49,291
- AND THE REST, FINGERS CROSSED
ON THE GUYS FROM A, B, AND C.

273
00:10:49,375 --> 00:10:52,458
- IT'S GONNA BE A ROUGH FIGHT,
NO MATTER WHAT.

274
00:10:52,541 --> 00:10:55,666
- YOU GUYS CAN LET ME HANDLE
LITTLE MISS TAKAHASHI.

275
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:57,750
KOUTA, WE'LL LEAVE OOSHIMA,
THE GYM TEACHER,

276
00:10:57,833 --> 00:10:59,750
FOR YOU TO HANDLE.
BEST OF LUCK.

277
00:10:59,833 --> 00:11:01,625
- ( grunts )

278
00:11:01,708 --> 00:11:04,958
- AND AKIHISA,
YOU'LL TAKE IRON MAN.

279
00:11:05,041 --> 00:11:05,958
- WHY ME?

280
00:11:06,041 --> 00:11:07,541
- BECAUSE YOU'RE
THE ONLY ONE HERE

281
00:11:07,625 --> 00:11:10,083
THAT HAS A PHYSICALLY ENHANCED 
AVATAR THAT CAN BRING HIM DOWN.

282
00:11:10,166 --> 00:11:11,750
- OKAY.

283
00:11:13,791 --> 00:11:15,750
- IF YOU DO THIS,

284
00:11:15,833 --> 00:11:18,041
WE'RE GONNA WATCH YOUR BACK
AT ALL COSTS.

285
00:11:18,125 --> 00:11:22,875
AND I GUARANTEE YOU, WE WILL
GET YOU TO IRON MAN UNSCATHED.

286
00:11:22,958 --> 00:11:25,791
AND WE'LL BE MORE THAN HAPPY
TO SACRIFICE OURSELVES.

287
00:11:25,875 --> 00:11:27,541
WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO MAKE CERTAIN THAT

288
00:11:27,625 --> 00:11:29,583
NO ONE EVEN TOUCHES YOU
BEFORE YOU'RE ABLE TO REACH HIM.

289
00:11:29,666 --> 00:11:32,125
- YOU MEAN IT?

290
00:11:32,208 --> 00:11:34,583
- WILL YOU PLEASE
DO THIS FOR US, AKIHISA?

291
00:11:34,666 --> 00:11:36,208
- FINE.

292
00:11:36,291 --> 00:11:37,958
- ( alarm rings, stops )

293
00:11:38,041 --> 00:11:39,708
- IT'S TIME TO LAUNCH
THE MISSION, GENTLEMEN.

294
00:11:39,791 --> 00:11:40,958
- RIGHT.
SO LET'S DO IT.

295
00:11:41,041 --> 00:11:42,541
ARE YOU GUYS
FIRED UP OR WHAT?

296
00:11:42,625 --> 00:11:43,958
- All: YEAH.

297
00:11:44,041 --> 00:11:46,083
- THIS IS OUR ONLY CHANCE.
- HUDDLE UP.

298
00:11:46,166 --> 00:11:47,583
- WE ACCEPT NOTHING LESS
THAN TOTAL VICTORY,

299
00:11:47,666 --> 00:11:48,708
AND NOTHING WILL STOP US
FROM ACHIEVING IT.

300
00:11:48,791 --> 00:11:50,541
- All: YEAH.

301
00:11:50,625 --> 00:11:52,833
- I DON'T CARE IF IT'S
GIRLS OR TEACHERS IN THERE.

302
00:11:52,916 --> 00:11:56,208
OUR EYES WILL FEAST UPON
A WET AND BUBBLY SKIN BUFFET.

303
00:11:56,291 --> 00:11:58,250
ON THE FOURTH NIGHT OF 
ACADEMIC TRAINING CAMP,

304
00:11:58,333 --> 00:12:02,500
WE SHALL OVERCOME!
LET'S GO.

305
00:12:05,791 --> 00:12:08,083
- ( Avatars grunting )
- THEY'RE HERE.

306
00:12:08,166 --> 00:12:10,166
THE FOUR PERVY MASTERMINDS.

307
00:12:10,250 --> 00:12:11,583
- THEY WON'T GET PAST US.

308
00:12:11,666 --> 00:12:13,000
- Both:
I'M SUMMONING MY AVATAR.

309
00:12:13,083 --> 00:12:14,916
SUMMON!

310
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:17,500
- ( Avatars shout )
- SUMMON!

311
00:12:17,583 --> 00:12:19,166
- ( grunts )

312
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:21,291
- DON'T KID YOURSELF,
CLASS F.

313
00:12:21,375 --> 00:12:24,416
- MAYBE YOU SHOULD
HIT THE BOOKS BEFORE YOU TALK.

314
00:12:24,500 --> 00:12:26,958
- ( grunts )
- ( both scream )

315
00:12:27,041 --> 00:12:29,083
- NO TIME TO WASTE 
ON THE SMALL FRIES.

316
00:12:29,166 --> 00:12:32,500
- THAT'S FAR ENOUGH.
NOW GIVE IT UP, YUUJI.

317
00:12:32,583 --> 00:12:35,458
- ( panting )
- AAH!

318
00:12:35,541 --> 00:12:36,958
- ( grunts )
- ( chuckles )

319
00:12:37,041 --> 00:12:38,458
- ( gasps )
- IT'S HIRAGA FROM CLASS D!

320
00:12:38,541 --> 00:12:40,291
THEY SHOWED!
- ALL RIGHT, GUYS.

321
00:12:40,375 --> 00:12:42,458
WE'LL HOLD THEM BACK.
KEEP MOVING.

322
00:12:42,541 --> 00:12:44,375
- ( Avatars shout )

323
00:12:44,458 --> 00:12:45,791
- THANKS A LOT, COMRADE.

324
00:12:45,875 --> 00:12:47,833
WE'LL SEE YOU IN VALHALLA.

325
00:12:47,916 --> 00:12:49,625
- ( moans )

326
00:12:51,625 --> 00:12:53,125
- THERE'S SO MUCH DEDICATION.

327
00:12:53,208 --> 00:12:54,708
- THAT'S 'CAUSE OUR
HEARTS ARE UNITED

328
00:12:54,791 --> 00:12:56,041
BEHIND ONE PURPOSE.

329
00:12:56,125 --> 00:12:57,875
- BUT OUR REAL BATTLE
STARTS HERE.

330
00:12:57,958 --> 00:12:59,916
- WE'RE SCREWED IF WE DON'T
HAVE ANY BACKUP THOUGH.

331
00:13:01,333 --> 00:13:03,333
- YOU BOYS NEVER LEARN!

332
00:13:03,416 --> 00:13:05,000
- ( Avatars grunt )

333
00:13:05,083 --> 00:13:07,083
- I'M SORRY, MR. FUSE.
THIS ISN'T PERSONAL.

334
00:13:07,166 --> 00:13:08,958
- NO, NOT YOU TOO.
TELL ME WHY.

335
00:13:09,041 --> 00:13:10,791
- IT'S KUROSAKI
FROM CLASS C!

336
00:13:10,875 --> 00:13:13,333
- KOUTA'S PICTURES HAD
A PROFOUND EFFECT ON ME.

337
00:13:13,416 --> 00:13:15,833
IN FACT, I'VE NEVER
CARED SO MUCH ABOUT ANYTHING

338
00:13:15,916 --> 00:13:17,500
IN MY ENTIRE LIFE.

339
00:13:17,583 --> 00:13:19,666
AND I PROMISE TO FIGHT
UNTIL THE BITTER END

340
00:13:19,750 --> 00:13:21,166
TO SEE SUCH BEAUTY
WITH MY OWN EYES. 

341
00:13:21,250 --> 00:13:24,125
- ( boys grunt )

342
00:13:24,208 --> 00:13:26,083
- WE COULDN'T HAVE GOTTEN
THIS FAR WITHOUT YOUR HELP.

343
00:13:26,166 --> 00:13:27,833
YOU GUYS WATCH OUR BACKS,
AND WE'LL DO OUR BEST

344
00:13:27,916 --> 00:13:29,583
TO CLEAR THE PATH.
- THANK YOU FOR GIVING ME

345
00:13:29,666 --> 00:13:31,250
A REASON TO DREAM AGAIN!

346
00:13:31,333 --> 00:13:33,750
MEN OF CLASS C, LET'S GIVE THEM
EVERY BIT OF THE SUPPORT

347
00:13:33,833 --> 00:13:35,750
THEY NEED.
THE GLORIOUS PATH TO VICTORY

348
00:13:35,833 --> 00:13:37,916
LIES STRAIGHT AHEAD.
- ( Class C boys cheer )

