FROM EVERY GUY 
IN EVERY CLASS.

352
00:13:43,166 --> 00:13:45,000
- TOO BAD CLASS A IS STILL
KIND OF A WILD CARD.

353
00:13:45,083 --> 00:13:47,416
- WE ALREADY KNOW THOSE PICTURES
WON'T WORK WITH KUBO.

354
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:49,708
- HOW IS THAT POSSIBLE?
DON'T TELL ME HE HAS

355
00:13:49,791 --> 00:13:51,625
