OF PICTURES THAN THOSE.

356
00:13:51,708 --> 00:13:54,041
- ( all sigh )

357
00:13:54,125 --> 00:13:55,708
- WELL, WELL, WELL,
IT TOOK YOU LONG ENOUGH.

358
00:13:55,791 --> 00:13:57,625
- LOOKS LIKE WE'VE GOT
