- YUUJI,
IT IS TIME TO GIVE UP.

362
00:14:06,208 --> 00:14:08,125
- SHOUKO.
- HIMEJI.

363
00:14:08,208 --> 00:14:10,875
- WE'RE NOT LETTING YOU
GET PAST THIS POINT, AKIHISA.

364
00:14:10,958 --> 00:14:12,541
- THAT'S IT.
