376
00:14:36,250 --> 00:14:37,750
NOW GET UP!
GET UP FOR BOOBIES!

377
00:14:37,833 --> 00:14:39,250
- LOOK, AKIHISA,

378
00:14:39,333 --> 00:14:41,166
THERE'S NO WAY WE CAN
WIN AT THIS POINT,

379
