ABOUT MY FEELINGS.

392
00:15:14,125 --> 00:15:15,875
SO I HAVE TO BE HONEST,

393
00:15:15,958 --> 00:15:19,291
AND THE TRUTH IS, THE ONLY
REASON THAT I'M DOING THIS

