404
00:15:44,125 --> 00:15:46,416
- I COULDN'T AGREE MORE,
AKIHISA.

405
00:15:46,500 --> 00:15:48,416
- HEY, WHO SAID THAT?
- ( gasps )

406
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:51,041
- I'M SORRY IT
TOOK US SO LONG,

407
00:15:51,125 --> 00:15:52,541
