BELIEVER IN YOUR CAUSE.

412
00:16:03,291 --> 00:16:06,083
THE GUYS OF CLASS A
STAND 24 STRONG,

413
00:16:06,166 --> 00:16:07,666
AND FROM NOW ON,
YOU HAVE OUR COMPLETE

414
00:16:07,750 --> 00:16:09,250
AND UNDYING ASSISTANCE.

415
00:16:09,333 --> 00:16:11,250
