GIVE HIM THE COVER HE NEEDS.

416
00:16:11,333 --> 00:16:12,833
- Class A Boys: YEAH!

417
00:16:12,916 --> 00:16:14,458
- THANK YOU, KUBO.
I OWE YOU ONE.

418
00:16:14,541 --> 00:16:16,916
- I'M THE ONE WHO SHOULD
BE THANKING YOU.

419
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:18,416
YOU WERE RIGHT
EARLIER ON.

420
00:16:18,500 --> 00:16:20,500
I CAN'T LIE ABOUT
MY FEELINGS EITHER.

421
00:16:20,583 --> 00:16:22,583
AND WHILE SOCIETY MAY
LOOK DOWN UPON ME,

422
00:16:22,666 --> 00:16:24,916
THE HEART WANTS
WHAT THE HEART WANTS!

423
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,666
- THIS IS BETWEEN
ME AND AKIHISA.

424
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:28,250
