FOR ALL OF YOU.

436
00:16:49,541 --> 00:16:51,000
SUMMON!

437
00:16:51,083 --> 00:16:53,833
- NO WAY.
WE'RE WALKING RIGHT THROUGH.!

438
00:16:57,875 --> 00:16:59,500
- ( gasps )

439
00:16:59,583 --> 00:17:02,708
( gasps )

440
00:17:02,791 --> 00:17:04,541
- UH--
- GO! 

441
00:17:04,625 --> 00:17:05,875
YOU CAN DO IT!

442
00:17:05,958 --> 00:17:08,250
- ( panting )

443
00:17:08,333 --> 00:17:09,708
- SUMMON!

444
00:17:09,791 --> 00:17:11,875
- ( grunts )

445
00:17:11,958 --> 00:17:13,458
- AAH!

446
00:17:13,541 --> 00:17:15,916
- ( gasps )
- NOTHING'S GONNA STOP HIM NOW.

447
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:19,083
- ( gasps )

448
00:17:19,166 --> 00:17:21,833
- WELL, IT'S ABOUT TIME.
I WAS STARTING TO THINK 

449
00:17:21,916 --> 00:17:23,916
YOU WEREN'T GONNA BE
ABLE TO MAKE IT, KOUTA.

450
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,916
- THEY WERE EXPECTING YOU.

451
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,833
- THERE'S NO CHANGE
IN OUR GAME PLAN.

452
00:17:27,916 --> 00:17:29,833
KEEP GOING, AKI.
- I CAN'T.

453
00:17:29,916 --> 00:17:31,333
- SURE, GO.
- ( gasps )

454
00:17:31,416 --> 00:17:33,500
- I'LL LET YOU PASS,
BUT ONLY IF KOUTA

455
00:17:33,583 --> 00:17:35,625
STAYS AND FACES ME.
- OH, FINE.

456
00:17:35,708 --> 00:17:37,708
- ALL RIGHT.

457
00:17:37,791 --> 00:17:40,000
GOOD LUCK NOT DYING,
MY BROTHER.

458
00:17:40,083 --> 00:17:43,583
- I AM BEYOND DISAPPOINTED
IN YOU, KID.

459
00:17:43,666 --> 00:17:45,250
DON'T TELL ME
YOU HONESTLY THINK

460
00:17:45,333 --> 00:17:46,583
A STUDENT CAN
BEAT A TEACHER.

461
00:17:46,666 --> 00:17:48,583
- WHO SAYS?

462
00:17:48,666 --> 00:17:50,333
- WHAT?

463
00:17:50,416 --> 00:17:52,250
- WHO SAYS THAT
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE

464
00:17:52,333 --> 00:17:54,666
FOR A STUDENT TO
DEFEAT A TEACHER?!

465
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:56,750
- VERY WELL.
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU WANT.

466
00:17:56,833 --> 00:17:58,166
- All: SUMMON!

467
00:17:58,250 --> 00:17:59,333
- ( grunts )

468
00:18:03,666 --> 00:18:05,625
- 774?!

469
00:18:05,708 --> 00:18:07,541
NOBODY'S EVER
SCORED THAT HIGH.

470
00:18:07,625 --> 00:18:09,666
HOW'D YOU DO THAT?
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

471
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:12,375
- HAVING FAITH RENDERS
ANYTHING POSSIBLE.

472
00:18:12,458 --> 00:18:15,125
- BUT HOW?  AND WHEN DID YOU
GAIN THAT MUCH STRENGTH?

473
00:18:15,208 --> 00:18:16,791
- OUR TIME IS RUNNING OUT.

474
00:18:16,875 --> 00:18:18,625
SO COME AT ME TOGETHER 
IF YOU'RE GONNA ATTACK.

475
00:18:18,708 --> 00:18:20,500
- ( both grunt )

476
00:18:26,583 --> 00:18:28,333
- ( grunts )
AAH!

477
00:18:28,416 --> 00:18:30,541
- I'M KIND OF SHOCKED
YOU ACTUALLY EXPECTED ME

478
00:18:30,625 --> 00:18:32,791
TO MAKE IT THIS FAR.
- I MAKE A POINT

479
00:18:32,875 --> 00:18:34,958
OF NEVER UNDERESTIMATING
MY OPPONENT.

480
00:18:35,041 --> 00:18:36,458
AND WHILE YOU'RE AN IDIOT,

481
00:18:36,541 --> 00:18:38,875
YOUR TENACITY IS
EXTRAORDINARY.

482
00:18:38,958 --> 00:18:40,416
- I APPRECIATE THAT.

483
00:18:40,500 --> 00:18:42,500
LET MET TAKE
THIS CHANCE TO THANK YOU!

484
00:18:42,583 --> 00:18:44,541
AND BY THE WAY,
YOU'RE PRETTY GOOD TOO.

485
00:18:44,625 --> 00:18:46,208
- AAH!

486
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:49,083
( grunts )

487
00:18:49,166 --> 00:18:51,750
- ( gasps )
- DON'T PATRONIZE ME, YOU TWERP.

488
00:18:51,833 --> 00:18:54,666
- AAH!
- ( screams )

489
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:56,583
( grunts )

490
00:18:56,666 --> 00:18:58,250
- DON'T PISS ME OFF, KID.

491
00:18:58,333 --> 00:19:00,000
I'M A LOT STRONGER
THAN THIS.

492
00:19:00,083 --> 00:19:01,625
- PROVE IT.

493
00:19:04,583 --> 00:19:07,083
GO ON AND GET UPSET.
LET'S DO THIS FOR REAL.

494
00:19:07,166 --> 00:19:08,875
- YA!
- ( grunts )

495
00:19:10,833 --> 00:19:12,583
YOU KNOW...

496
00:19:12,666 --> 00:19:14,666
YOU'RE GONNA GET SUSPENDED
IF YOU WALK THROUGH THAT DOOR.

497
00:19:14,750 --> 00:19:16,250
- I'M NOT TOO
WORRIED ABOUT IT.

498
00:19:16,333 --> 00:19:18,000
THERE ARE WAY TOO MANY
OF US TO CATCH.

499
00:19:18,083 --> 00:19:19,666
YOU WON'T EVEN KNOW
WHO TO SUSPEND.

500
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:22,083
- REALLY?  YOU CAN'T
HONESTLY BELIEVE THAT.

501
00:19:22,166 --> 00:19:25,458
- ( gasps )
- DON'T DROP YOUR GUARD!

502
00:19:25,541 --> 00:19:27,416
( grunts )
- NO!

503
00:19:27,500 --> 00:19:29,125
- IF THERE'S THAT MANY OF YOU,

504
00:19:29,208 --> 00:19:30,708
WE'LL JUST HAVE TO
KICK YOUR ASSES

505
00:19:30,791 --> 00:19:32,750
AND TAKE OUR TIME
IDENTIFYING YOU! 

506
00:19:32,833 --> 00:19:34,041
- ( both gasp )

507
00:19:34,125 --> 00:19:35,541
- AAH!

508
00:19:35,625 --> 00:19:37,583
- ( both grunting )

509
00:19:41,375 --> 00:19:44,333
- AND NOW WE'RE DONE.
SO GIVE UP.

510
00:19:44,416 --> 00:19:45,875
- WHAT CAN I DO?

511
00:19:45,958 --> 00:19:49,000
I'VE GOT TO BEAT THIS GUY.

512
00:19:49,083 --> 00:19:54,291
- YOU SIMPLY LACK THE FOCUS TO
EXECUTE SUCH A COMPLICATED PLAN.

513
00:19:54,375 --> 00:19:57,291
- I TRIED SO HARD,
BUT I DON'T KNOW. 

514
00:19:57,375 --> 00:19:58,458
MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.

515
00:19:58,541 --> 00:20:00,583
I SIMPLY LACK--
THAT'S IT!

516
00:20:00,666 --> 00:20:03,041
YEAH.  FOCUS.

517
00:20:03,125 --> 00:20:04,625
IF I NARROW THE AIM,

518
00:20:04,708 --> 00:20:07,041
IF I FIGHT ALONGSIDE MY AVATAR,

519
00:20:07,125 --> 00:20:10,333
WE CAN CONCENTRATE OUR ATTACKS
TO A SINGLE SPOT ON YOUR BODY.

520
00:20:10,416 --> 00:20:12,750
WE'LL FOCUS OUR ATTACKS
ON YOUR BALLS!

521
00:20:12,833 --> 00:20:15,333
- WHAT?!  THAT IS
A GENUINELY DISTURBING IDEA

522
00:20:15,416 --> 00:20:16,833
FOR YOU TO EVEN THINK OF.

523
00:20:16,916 --> 00:20:19,208
- PASS OUT AND SAVE YOURSELF
A LITTLE PAIN!

524
00:20:19,291 --> 00:20:22,208
- AAH!
- KISS YOUR BALLS GOOD-BYE!

525
00:20:22,291 --> 00:20:24,916
- ( gasps )
- I'M JUST MESSING WITH YOU.

526
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:28,000
- ( bones crack )
- ( chuckles )

527
00:20:28,083 --> 00:20:29,083
- ( gasps )

528
00:20:32,583 --> 00:20:34,375
- SUCKER.
( gasps )

529
00:20:35,958 --> 00:20:37,833
- AH!
- ( gasps )

530
00:20:37,916 --> 00:20:41,083
- I REFUSE TO LET YOU
DEFLOWER MY LOVE.

531
00:20:41,166 --> 00:20:43,166
- MIHARU?
- CALL IT QUITS,

532
00:20:43,250 --> 00:20:46,541
OR OTHERWISE I'LL SPREAD THIS
PICTURE AROUND LIKE THE PLAGUE

533
00:20:46,625 --> 00:20:48,291
AND YOU WILL NEVER
EVER BE POPULAR.

534
00:20:48,375 --> 00:20:50,958
- YOU'VE GOT MY PICTURE?
I'M GONNA GO OUT ON A LIMB HERE.

535
00:20:51,041 --> 00:20:53,000
DO YOU HAVE A BURN MARK
ON YOUR BUTT?

536
00:20:55,291 --> 00:20:56,958
- HOW DO YOU KNOW ABOUT THAT?

537
00:20:57,041 --> 00:20:59,541
- SO YOU'VE BEEN THE ONE
BLACKMAILING ME THIS WHOLE TIME?

538
00:20:59,625 --> 00:21:00,916
WHICH MEANS THAT
THE HIDDEN CAMERA

539
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,541
IN THE LOCKER ROOM IS YOURS.

540
00:21:02,625 --> 00:21:05,541
- GOOD JOB FIGURING IT OUT,
BUT NOW I HAVE TO KILL YOU.

541
00:21:05,625 --> 00:21:07,333
WAY TO GO, SMART GUY.

542
00:21:07,416 --> 00:21:10,000
- YOU DID IT, MAN.
VERY NICE.

543
00:21:10,083 --> 00:21:13,041
- AWESOME.  YOU GUYS ALL
MADE IT OUT ALIVE.

544
00:21:13,125 --> 00:21:15,375
- OF COURSE.
- IF WE STORM THE BATHING ROOM

545
00:21:15,458 --> 00:21:17,458
WITH THIS MANY PEOPLE,
THEY'RE NEVER GONNA BE ABLE

546
00:21:17,541 --> 00:21:19,041
TO CATCH ALL OF US.
- EXACTLY.

547
00:21:19,125 --> 00:21:20,541
THERE'S NO WAY THEY CAN
PUNISH US

548
00:21:20,625 --> 00:21:22,541
IF WE ALL RUSH IN TOGETHER.
LET'S GO.

549
00:21:22,625 --> 00:21:24,208
- All: YEAH!

550
00:21:24,291 --> 00:21:26,125
- Fukuhara: A DIFFICULT
AND PAINFUL BATTLE

551
00:21:26,208 --> 00:21:28,250
FROM WHICH THEY
ARISE VICTORIOUS.

552
00:21:28,333 --> 00:21:30,750
WITH NO ONE LEFT TO
STAND IN THEIR WAY,

553
00:21:30,833 --> 00:21:34,125
THE MEN MARCH FORWARD
WITH PRIDE IN THEIR HEARTS.

554
00:21:34,208 --> 00:21:36,500
- ( all gasp )

555
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:41,583
- WHAT THE HELL DO YOU BOYS
THINK YOU'RE DOING?

556
00:21:41,666 --> 00:21:44,291
- Boys: ( gasping )
IT WAS ALL FOR NOTHING?!

557
00:21:47,083 --> 00:21:48,666
- Fukuhara:
"ALL YEAR TWO MALE STUDENTS

558
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:52,250
IN FUMIZUKI ACADEMY,
A TOTAL OF 149,

559
00:21:52,333 --> 00:21:54,666
ARE TO BE SUSPENDED
FROM SCHOOL FOR A WEEK."

560
00:21:57,500 --> 00:21:59,791
- ( theme music playing )
- ( singing in Japanese )

561
00:23:15,166 --> 00:23:16,458
- Fukuhara: BAKA AND TEST.

562
00:23:22,583 --> 00:23:24,166
- Mizuki: AKIHISA!

563
00:23:24,250 --> 00:23:26,000
- HEY.  LONG TIME, NO SEE,
HIMEJI.

564
00:23:26,083 --> 00:23:28,916
HOW HAVE YOU BEEN DOING?
- I JUST WANTED TO TELL YOU

565
00:23:29,000 --> 00:23:31,375
I'M REALLY SORRY.
- WHAT, BUT WHY? 

566
00:23:31,458 --> 00:23:34,125
- I FEEL SO TERRIBLE FOR
TREATING YOU LIKE A PEEPING TOM

567
00:23:34,208 --> 00:23:36,791
ON THE FIRST DAY OF
ACADEMIC TRAINING CAMP.

568
00:23:36,875 --> 00:23:38,875
PLEASE FORGIVE ME.
- WELL, TO BE FAIR,

569
00:23:38,958 --> 00:23:40,541
ALL YOU DID WAS CALL IT
BEFORE IT HAPPENED,

570
00:23:40,625 --> 00:23:43,208
SO NO BIG DEAL.
- AKI!

571
00:23:43,291 --> 00:23:45,833
- HEY, MINAMI.
WHAT'S UP?

572
00:23:52,208 --> 00:23:53,875
- Fukuhara: QUESTION EIGHT.

573
00:23:53,958 --> 00:23:56,625
WHAT WERE YOUR ASPIRATIONS
WHEN YOU ENTERED THE ACADEMY?

574
00:23:56,708 --> 00:23:58,291
- Akihisa: I BELIEVED
THAT I WAS SPECIAL,

575
00:23:58,375 --> 00:24:00,083
AND THAT ONE DAY OTHERS WOULD
REALIZE MY TRUE TALENTS.

576
00:24:00,166 --> 00:24:01,666
- Fukuhara: GET REAL, KID.

577
00:24:01,750 --> 00:24:04,125
- Akihisa: NEXT TIME,
ME, JAPAN, AND UNKNOWN WORDS!

578
00:24:04,208 --> 00:24:06,083
- Fukuhara:
THIS WILL BE ON THE TEST.

